        {"name": "Prof. Muratović", "text": "Danas razmatramo Chalmersa i hard problem of consciousness. Zašto je to 'teški' problem, za razliku od 'lakih' problema?", "translation": "Today we consider Chalmers and the hard problem of consciousness. Why is it the 'hard' problem, as opposed to the 'easy' problems?"},
        {"name": "Doktorandica Begić", "text": "Laki problemi — poput objašnjenja pažnje, pamćenja, ili diskriminacije podražaja — mogu se riješiti funkcionalnim opisom. Ali tvrdi problem pita: zašto uopće ima subjektivnog iskustva?", "translation": "The easy problems — such as explaining attention, memory, or stimulus discrimination — can be solved by functional description. But the hard problem asks: why is there subjective experience at all?"},
        {"name": "Prof. Muratović", "text": "Tačno. Čak i da bismo savršeno opisali sve neuralne korelate, ostaje pitanje: zašto te neuralne aktivnosti 'izgledaju' nekako iznutra?", "translation": "Exactly. Even if we perfectly described all neural correlates, the question remains: why do those neural activities 'look like' something from the inside?"},
